div.p:
The Enter a Name or Position box lets you quickly move
around the sky. Positions are in Right Ascension and Declination
(ICRS) and must be separated by a comma, otherwise
the text is sent to the 
LookUP
service to try and identify a location. The support
for positions is limited to the following formats:
205.842, -14.8367;
13 43 22, -14 50 12;
13:43:22, -14:50:12;
13h 43m 22s, -14d 50m 12s;
or
13h 43m 22s, -14d 50' 12".
